VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'should also read for clarification. Okay. After&nbsp; finishing the settings for our output video,&nbsp;&nbsp; we can preview the merged clips by running&nbsp; this node. You can see that a 2-second blank&nbsp;&nbsp;'

